    "markdown": "---\nformat:\n  html:\n    css: styles.css\n    embed-resources: TRUE\n    code-fold: true\n    page-layout: full\n    fig_caption: yes\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n::: narrow-section\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"grid-container\" style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); justify-items: center;\">\n<div id=\"highlight-text\">1,035</div>\n<div id=\"highlight-text\">2,595</div>\n<div style=\"display: block; &#10;              color: #ff6400; &#10;              font-size: 1.25em; &#10;              font-family: Graphik; &#10;              font-weight: bold; &#10;              text-align: center;\">Low<br>Indeterminacy</div>\n<div id=\"bold-text\">Currently Eligible for<br>Parole but in Prison</div>\n<div id=\"bold-text\">Eligible for Parole in<br>the next 1-5 years</div>\n<div id=\"bold-text\">\n<span class=\"tippy html-widget html-fill-item-overflow-hidden html-fill-item\" height=\"338px\" id=\"htmlwidget-224f440730a59dff9c0f\" width=\"100%\"></span>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-224f440730a59dff9c0f\">{\"x\":{\"opts\":{\"placement\":\"bottom\",\"flip\":true,\"theme\":\"light\",\"content\":\"To compare the degrees of indeterminacy, or unpredictability\\n   of time served, of prison-sentencing systems of different jurisdictions,\\n   we use a qualitative ranking framework based on the Robina Institute's\\n   Prison-release Discretion And Prison Population Size Report.<br><br><b>Low Indeterminacy<\\/b>: >20-40 percent indeterminacy (first prospect of release at 60-79.99 percent of judicial maximum).\"},\"text\":\"<span aria-label=\\\"To compare the degrees of indeterminacy, or unpredictability\\n   of time served, of prison-sentencing systems of different jurisdictions,\\n   we use a qualitative ranking framework based on the Robina Institute's\\n   Prison-release Discretion And Prison Population Size Report.<br><br><b>Low Indeterminacy<\\/b>: